name: The Adventures of Jane Jelly: The Treasure of Zedin
overview: You are Jane Jelly, a treasure hunter. Your mission is to explore the caves of Spectrum and find the treasure of Zedin! Besides the treasure you will find 25 valuable relics. Also you have to find 3 keys. Open the doors with the number of keys requested. But your task will not be easy...in your way you will find many cave hazards that could kill you.
